  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Providing life-saving humanitarian relief to communities affected by shocks in Somalia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to support 1,270 drought affected communities from Sool, Sanaag, and Bari regions of Puntland. The programme will adapt a community based approach and will target current displaced populations and poor host communities in the target areas. Based on identified needs in the target locations, the proposed action focuses on food security/livelihoods. The primary demographic focus is women and children.</narrative>
  </description>
